Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.59,0:01:06.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Squeez'n step on it hard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.59,0:01:06.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}跨上機車 馬力全開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:09.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try to feet my heart beat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:09.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}試著去感受心的律動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.36,0:01:12.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,High,as high as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.36,0:01:12.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}飛躍吧！盡你所能！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.99,0:01:16.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All your blood will turn to fountain water
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.99,0:01:16.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}血液沸騰有如泉湧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.49,0:01:19.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded by plot in this universe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.49,0:01:19.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大千世界，我們的週遭佈滿陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:23.64,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wash away the stain of blood with tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:23.64,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}用淚水洗去血染的污點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:26.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot look,or they will spell on you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:26.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}讓雙眼避開所有的蠱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:30.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wind of fuego will lead us through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:30.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"烈焰"之風會引領我們向前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.28,0:01:47.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.28,0:01:47.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真實 我與它們融與一體
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.52,0:01:51.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found guide-in line in the raging world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.52,0:01:51.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在波濤洶湧的世界裡找尋指引
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:55.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:55.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}舉目看 天湛藍 縱然世界狂亂不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:01:56.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ride on Back
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:01:56.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}仍有背騎的身影穿梭其間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:01:59.71,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All we need is your sympathy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:01:59.71,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我們需要的是你們的共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.73,0:02:02.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We make the history of our own
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.73,0:02:02.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一同去創造屬於我們的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.98,0:02:06.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.98,0:02:06.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真實 我與它們融與一體
